name: Look Me In The Eyes
description:
Final piece of my black and white 35mm film serie.

I remember the countless tests that I did in the darkroom to get this photo right. Needless to say that I was extremely happy with the final result! Also, here's a little backstory, this person is actually my ex. Good thing that we're still friends or this photo could've met a less positive fate.

Funny enough, I also noticed that I have a bad habit of avoiding eye contact when I talk to people. Thank you anxiety lol.

4x6
Analogue camera
black and white 35mm film
